Bakso Simulator (Meatball Simulator)

Credit = Andy Lukito = https://www.youtube.com/@AndyLukito Download Game At= itch.io= https://razkha.itch.io/bakso-simulator
Have you ever dreamed of owning your own meatball business? Dream no more, now you can with Bakso Simulator! In this world, you'll open a bakso business with your old friend, while helping the townspeople and solving all the mysteries!


Build your business!

Upgrade your business!

And protect your business!

Features :
Build your own meatball business
Improve the quality of your meatballs, expand your cart, and increase your business rating
Finished work? You can go home to a house that can be designed according to your taste
Carts and shophouses can also be decorated according to your wishes
Many characters and secrets in this city
Follow the storyline of this game which is full of surprises
Don't forget to pay all your employees
Protect your business from flies, thieves and ghosts
Most importantly, collect as much money as possible and make your meatball business the best on earth!

MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:

OS*: Windows 7 (SP1+), Windows 10 and Windows 11 Processor: x86, x64 architecture with SSE2 instruction set support Graphics: DX10, DX11, DX12 capable DirectX: Version 10 Storage: 1 GB available space
